OL,7,FThe shortage of penicillin to treat
OL,8,Fstrep A infections is so acute that
OL,9,Fpharmacists are being advised to give
OL,10,Fchildren solid tablets if they cannot
OL,11,Fprovide the liquid form, it has
OL,12,Femerged.
